System on a Chip Units (SoCs)
System on a chip units (SoCs) produced by NVIDIA cater to mobile computing and automotive markets.

California
California is the state where NVIDIA Corporation is headquartered, specifically in Santa Clara.

NVIDIA Corporation
NVIDIA Corporation is a multinational technology company, incorporated in Delaware and based in Santa Clara, California. The company is known for designing graphics processing units (GPUs) and system on a chip units (SoCs) for various markets.

Graphics Processing Units (GPUs)
Graphics processing units (GPUs) designed by NVIDIA appeal to both gaming and professional markets.

Data Center Demand
Data center demand represents a significant area of business for NVIDIA Corporation, driven by advancements in technology and increased reliance on data centers.

Delaware
Delaware is the state where NVIDIA Corporation is incorporated.

Artificial Intelligence (AI)
Artificial intelligence (AI) is a key area of focus for NVIDIA Corporation, reflecting its leadership in the industry.
